::Ice::

She felt her head pound like it was about to split open. She clitched her 
head with her paws. "Ohhhh, this hurts." She tried to close her mind to the 
thoughts of others.  She managed to close it off but to two bots, Veratis 
and Lunarpine.  She sent a message to Veratis, "Got Asperin?" She shook her 
head and resent a message. "What are the orders? What's the mission?" Her 
mind was threating to shut down and close the mind reading program.  She 
fought it, but her headache wasn't helping her any. She reopened her mind 
and started to hear the thoughts of the bots around her. Though it was 
unintentional.
